OL,6,FJurors have been shown dramatic video
OL,7,Fof the moment fugitive aristocrat
OL,8,FConstance Marten was arrested in the
OL,9,Fstreet and asked repeatedly: "Where is
OL,10,Fyour child?"
OL,12,FConstance Marten, 36, and Mark Gordon,
OL,13,F49, had allegedly been living with
OL,14,Ftheir newborn baby off grid in a tent
OL,15,Fon the South Downs while on the run
OL,16,Ffrom police.
OL,18,FLast February 27, police finally
OL,19,Ftracked them down to the Hollingbury
OL,20,Farea of Brighton after they were
OL,21,Fspotted by a member of the public.
