OL,6,FThey declined to say where baby
OL,7,FVictoria was and on March 1, her body
OL,8,Fwas found in a Lidl supermarket bag
OL,9,Fcovered in rubbish in a disused shed.
OL,11,FPolice Sergeant Robert Button was
OL,12,Famong the officers who arrested the
OL,13,Fdefendants at 9.35pm last February 27.
OL,15,FGiving evidence, Mr Button said Marten
OL,16,Fappeared to be wearing "furniture
OL,17,Fstuffing" for insulation and smelled
OL,18,F"unclean and unwashed".
