OL,6,FWhen Gordon denied it, he was asked
OL,7,Fwhy he was running away and ordered
OL,8,Frepeatedly to put the stick he was
OL,9,Fcarrying down.
OL,11,FAs the defendant resisted, he was
OL,12,Ftold: "Relax yourself, you are under
OL,13,Farrest until I confirm who you are."
OL,15,FGordon complained he was hungry and he
OL,16,F"wasn't doing anything".
OL,18,FA distressed Marten then intervened
OL,19,Fsaying: "Stop with him please, he's
OL,20,Fnot well."
