OL,6,FShe went on: "Oh my god, I can't
OL,7,Fwatch. Leave him alone. Let him eat
OL,8,Fhis food. He's starving."
OL,10,FAnother officer later turned to Marten
OL,11,Fand said: "I'll level with you, you
OL,12,Fare under arrest for child neglect."
OL,14,FMarten replied: "For doing what?"
OL,16,FShe was then asked by officers:
OL,17,F"Where's your child? Where's your
OL,18,Fchild? Sorry, where is your child, we
OL,19,Fneed to know?"
OL,21,FThe defendant did not respond.
