OL,6,FThey became front-page news last
OL,7,FJanuary when Greater Manchester Police
OL,8,Flaunched a missing persons inquiry
OL,9,Fafter finding a placenta in the
OL,10,Fcouple's burnt-out car on a motorway
OL,11,Fnear Bolton.
OL,13,FLast February 20, the defendants had
OL,14,Fbeen caught on camera trying to break
OL,15,Finto Hollingbury Golf Course near
OL,16,FBrighton, East Sussex, and "rumaging"
OL,17,Fthrough a wheelie bin, the court heard.
OL,19,FOn the evening of February 27, CCTV
OL,20,Fcaptured Marten appearing to attempt
OL,21,Fto steal food from a shop.
