OL,6,FShe then withdrew cash from an ATM
OL,7,Fmachine and Gordon bought food in a
OL,8,Fconvenience store.
OL,10,FResident Dale Cooley spotted Gordon
OL,11,Fcarrying a stick with one foot wrapped
OL,12,Fin a plastic bag, which he thought was
OL,13,F"strange".
OL,15,FMr Cooley recognised the couple and
OL,16,Fchecked a story on the local Argus
OL,17,Fnewspaper website to confirm his
OL,18,Fsuspicions.
