OL,6,FHe described phoning his wife, saying:
OL,7,F"I told her it was definitely the
OL,8,Fcouple from the news because the
OL,9,Fdescriptions matched and their
OL,10,Fbehaviour seemed strange as if they
OL,11,Fwere trying to stay hidden."
OL,13,FHe tried to engage them in
OL,14,Fconversation asking if they were on
OL,15,FStanmer Drive, and Gordon replied "we
OL,16,Fdon't know" in a gruff Northern
OL,17,Faccent, the court was told.
