OL,6,FIn a statement read to court, Mr
OL,7,FCooley said: "Their body language
OL,8,Fsuggested they did not want to be
OL,9,Fbothered. I spotted a paramedic car
OL,10,Fand waved them down. I asked them what
OL,11,FI should do and they said call 999."
OL,13,FMr Cooley, who had gone out in his car
OL,14,Fto dispose of coffee pots and visit an
OL,15,FATM, alerted police at 9.26pm.
OL,17,FThe defendants, of no fixed address,
OL,18,Fdeny the manslaughter of baby Victoria
OL,19,Fby gross negligence between January 4
OL,20,Fand February 27 last year.
